                                            ehemals.</note></seg></foreign> St. Anne, No. 66</hi>
                            <foreign xml:lang="fra"><space unit="section"/></foreign><hi rendition="#aq"><foreign xml:lang="fra"><seg type="comment"><orig>au
                                            coin de</orig><note xml:id="nbmr_pyp_nsb">Frz.: an der
                                            Ecke zu.</note></seg></foreign> celle
                                Neuve-Augustin</hi><lb/><hi rendition="#aq">
                                <hi rendition="#c">a Paris<anchor type="target" xml:id="stop_tll_jg5_4sb"/></hi>
                            </hi></seg>
                    </signed>
